	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />EVVAIII!!! <delay20 />GRANDEEE!!!<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><10_9 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Dai, un po' di tifo! <delay8 />Mica soltanto i
